      <section id="id2394710">
        <title>Assessment Standard</title>
        <para id="id2370645">We know this when the learner:</para>
        <para id="id4281150">3.1 identifies issues associated with resources and services in a particular  context;</para>
        <para id="id3508466">3.2 identifies the factors that influence why some people have better access to resources compared to others in a particular context;</para>
